      "team.zeynalov_bio":             "<p>Zeynalov Elshan is the founder and Managing Director of PROBIZ LEGAL HUB LLC, with over 20 years of professional experience in commercial and corporate law. Widely recognised for his deep expertise in complex arbitration disputes and contract law, he ensures his clients' business interests are protected to the highest professional standards.</p><p>Company formation, structuring, and the successful resolution of commercial disputes are among his core specialisations.</p>",
      "team.abdullayeva_bio":          "<p>Abdullayeva Arzu is a dedicated legal counsel specialising in legal document drafting and litigation preparation. She has 3 years of professional experience in drafting documents, conducting pre-litigation research, and analysing client inquiries in civil and corporate law.</p><p>Her meticulous attention to detail and responsible approach have made her an indispensable member of the team.</p>",
      "team.babazade_bio":             "<p>Babazade Ilgar is a professional expert with 25 years of extensive experience in HR administration and labour legislation. The correct management of human resources, recruitment, and the legal resolution of labour disputes form the core of his work.</p><p>He specialises in conducting HR audits within companies and building HR systems.</p>",
      "team.mammedova_bio":            "<p>Mammadova Shovkat is responsible for shaping HR policy in line with the company's strategic objectives. Over 20 years of professional activity, she has achieved significant results in organisational development, personnel management, and business partnership.</p><p>She bridges leadership and staff, making a meaningful contribution to the development of corporate culture.</p>",
      "team.zeynalova_bio":            "<p>Zeynalova Gulshen is a professional manager with 23 years of rich experience in workforce planning, selection, and performance monitoring. She plays a decisive role in growing the company's talent pool and attracting new talent.</p><p>Her exceptional communication skills have a significant positive impact on team spirit and employee satisfaction within the company.</p>",
      "team.eliyev_bio":               "<p>Aliyev Subhan is a court advocate with successful outcomes in public and administrative law, as well as criminal and tax law. With 20 years of professional experience, he is able to deeply protect his clients' interests even in the most complex legal situations.</p><p>His analytical qualities create the conditions for the flawless execution of strategy in the courtroom.</p>",
      "team.memmedli_bio":             "<p>Mammadli Lala is a young yet ambitious advocate who stands out for her high level of knowledge and experience in family, labour, customs, and public law. Despite just 5 years of professional experience, she has successfully applied her academic knowledge in practice, completing many challenging cases.</p><p>On the path towards an academic degree, Lala earns client trust through her individual and detailed approach to every case.</p>",
      "team.esgerov_bio":              "<p>Asgarov Khalig is a highly experienced advocate known for numerous successfully concluded civil, property, family, and labour disputes. His 24-year track record confirms his mastery of every nuance of the law.</p><p>In criminal, public, and administrative law too, he applies proactive defence methods and knows precisely how to gain advantage in court proceedings.</p>",

